        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "koenig-heading",
        "tag": "h3",
        "version": 1,
        "renderVersion": "4.0"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As stated in the intro, this is likely the most unique ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Dragon Ball",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " game on the market at the time of release. You do not directly play as any of the main cast of good guys from the series for about ninety percent of the game’s duration (there is a way to transform into Goku temporarily). The concept of playing as regular people while trying to survive beings that can and have destroyed entire planets puts the villains into a new perspective to the player. When you can’t trade blows with Freiza, you’re much less willing to let him find you. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "html": "<a href=\"https://powera.pxf.io/c/3324894/1258631/15385\" target=\"_top\" id=\"1258631\"><img src=\"//a.impactradius-go.com/display-ad/15385-1258631\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\"/></a><img height=\"0\" width=\"0\" src=\"https://imp.pxf.io/i/3324894/1258631/15385\" style=\"position:absolute;visibility:hidden;\" border=\"0\" />"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Unlike in titles like ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Dead by Daylight",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", the survivors are not entirely hopeless. You have access to some gear to help you, such as hover bikes to move about the map faster, a bounce pad to reach higher areas, a hover device to glide farther when falling, and more. They also have the ability to charge up and temporarily gain the abilities of one of the heroes of ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Dragon Ball",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to try and distract the “Raider” for a short time. All in all, it’s a breath of fresh air for the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Dragon Ball",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " series of games, as well as a new spin on the asymmetrical multiplayer genre itself.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
